{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回　勤修苦练：本章围绕主要人物的遭遇、江湖见闻与冲突推进展开。第二回勤修苦练秦淮河花肪笙歌，聚六朝金粉，此时已是子夜，但寻欢逐乐的公子阔少仍未散尽，熊倜走到河边，看到每只船上都挂着块牌子，上面写着名字，有些船灯火仍亮，里面有喧笑声，有些船却已熄了灯火，他看见有一只船停在较远之处，不像别的船那样一只连着一只，而且灯火仍然亮着，他就走了过去。那只船的窗户向外支着，他站在岸边看了一会儿，里面并无哗笑之声章节中人物往来、言语试探和武林局势互相交织，为后续恩怨、师承与行动埋下线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐姐真好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么你哭得我就哭不得呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "戴梦尧是你的师父？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你把戴梦尧教你的天雷行功练一遍给我看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已为你打通",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "记着。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弟子知道。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小姐姐早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐姐，我要走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ruo_lan",
      "speaker_name": "若兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还以为，你不……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ruo_lan",
      "speaker_name": "若兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐姐我走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ruo_lan",
      "speaker_name": "若兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "路上要小心呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我该先去莫愁湖，去看看戴叔叔和我分别的地方，然后呢……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那鸣远镖局在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他已死了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那萨天骥现在在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快往下躲。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "熊兄若是打听别的人物，只要是江湖上稍有名气的，小弟不敢说了如指掌，但也略知一二，但是这萨天骥么……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    }
  ],
